### Variables
@host = http://localhost:3000

### Health check
GET {{host}}/

### Trigger pipeline — send 1 best deal to configured group
POST {{host}}/pipeline/trigger
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "max": 1
}

### Trigger pipeline — custom params
POST {{host}}/pipeline/trigger
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "MLB1648",
  "minDiscount": 30,
  "max": 3
}

### Trigger pipeline — celulares (MLB1051)
POST {{host}}/pipeline/trigger
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "MLB1051",
  "minDiscount": 25,
  "max": 1
}

### Trigger pipeline — eletronicos (MLB1000)
POST {{host}}/pipeline/trigger
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "MLB1000",
  "minDiscount": 25,
  "max": 1
}

### Reload affiliate cache (after editing affiliate-links.json)
POST {{host}}/affiliate/reload

### Preview — list URLs bot WILL send. Paste these into ML affiliate panel to generate short links.
POST {{host}}/pipeline/preview
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "perCategory": 5,
  "minDiscount": 25
}

### Preview — single category only
POST {{host}}/pipeline/preview
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categories": ["MLB1648"],
  "perCategory": 10
}
